WARNING. The files in theis directory give away valuable information to the
game. DO NOT READ if you do not wish to be spoiled. The hint files are rot13'd
to prevent acidental viewing. However the source files slag creates are not.

Developers:
The following is an example use of the hints:

    Include "shell_hints";
    [ HintsSub; SLAG_RunMenus(); ];
    Verb "hint" "hints" * -> Hints;
